I am Trans: This play depicts a developing romantic relationship between a cisgender woman and a transgender man during his transition and uses it as a way to explore love in the queer community. Details: The play is on June 7 at the Baxter Theatre, Main Road, Rondebosch, Cape Town. Tickets cost R100 to R180 and can be purchased from Webtickets.
